WEBVTT

00:00.203 --> 00:01.710
<i>Previously, on "Bitten"...</i>

00:01.713 --> 00:04.859
You're always going to
be my little man, Clay.

00:04.898 --> 00:07.732
Man: You have to understand
them to fight them.

00:07.734 --> 00:09.300
That book is the key.

00:09.302 --> 00:10.502
Elena?

00:10.504 --> 00:12.404
You're going to die.

00:12.406 --> 00:15.006
Savannah: I keep having this
vision that you're getting killed.

00:15.008 --> 00:17.041
A premonition of something
that will happen.

00:17.043 --> 00:18.342
Aleister is there, too.

00:18.344 --> 00:20.011
Elena: Aleister is dead.

00:20.013 --> 00:23.080
By the end of the day, you
will kill Roman Navikev.

00:23.082 --> 00:24.448
I'm not going to kill the Russian Alpha

00:24.450 --> 00:26.918
and start a war
because you threatened me?

00:26.920 --> 00:28.552
Elena: But at Aleister's compound,

00:28.554 --> 00:31.923
when you were angry, you had
trouble controlling your power.

00:31.925 --> 00:33.524
(Screaming)

00:33.526 --> 00:34.925
Eduardo, he's in the forest.

00:34.927 --> 00:36.693
- Get him.
- I'm on it.

00:38.530 --> 00:39.797
(Groaning)

00:41.032 --> 00:42.132
(Grunt)

00:42.134 --> 00:43.700
You're chasing the wrong enemy.

00:43.702 --> 00:45.368
Clay: We killed you!

00:45.370 --> 00:48.171
Aleister: With your help,
I'll get what I need.

00:48.173 --> 00:51.673
( ♪ )

00:57.614 --> 01:03.053
Woman: (Incantation in foreign language)

01:03.055 --> 01:06.889
(Mixed eerie whispers)

01:13.664 --> 01:15.565
Enjoy the heart attack, Charlie.

01:22.238 --> 01:24.406
Ruth: Clara, stop!

01:24.408 --> 01:26.208
This isn't what it looks like, Ruthie.

01:26.210 --> 01:27.476
Then what?

01:27.478 --> 01:28.777
Because it looks like
you're killing people.

01:28.779 --> 01:30.479
Look, I need the money. All right?

01:30.481 --> 01:32.014
Trust me, these guys are no saints.

01:32.016 --> 01:33.515
You crossed a line, Clara.

01:33.517 --> 01:36.852
Please... Please. Ruth...

01:36.854 --> 01:38.153
I'll go back to the ways of the Coven.

01:38.155 --> 01:39.855
I'll serve you. Whatever you want.

01:39.857 --> 01:42.156
This is not a negotiation.

01:42.158 --> 01:44.258
(Screaming)

01:44.260 --> 01:47.362
<i>Amoletum ad pulverem.</i>

01:47.364 --> 01:52.133
(Eerie music)

01:53.335 --> 01:54.836
(Gasping)

01:58.773 --> 02:00.808
You'll pay for this.

02:00.810 --> 02:03.311
(Panting)

02:03.313 --> 02:06.347
Aleister: All is not as it
may seem on the surface.

02:06.349 --> 02:09.616
It is what's inside of
you that is the truth.

02:09.619 --> 02:15.689
But, it's your essence,
your history, your future.

02:19.694 --> 02:22.462
Every drop you have

02:22.464 --> 02:25.465
moves through your whole body

02:25.467 --> 02:26.800
in a minute.

02:29.737 --> 02:31.471
(Gasping)

02:31.473 --> 02:32.672
(Mixed murmurs of crowd)

02:32.674 --> 02:36.443
You don't want to lose any of it.

02:36.445 --> 02:38.011
(Applause)

02:38.013 --> 02:39.346
Clara: Timothy!

02:43.251 --> 02:46.920
(Indistinct chatter)

02:50.257 --> 02:51.524
Who are you?

02:51.526 --> 02:53.560
I'm the reason you're alive.

02:55.429 --> 02:59.465
Then you must know what I am.

02:59.467 --> 03:01.233
You're the prophecy.

03:01.235 --> 03:03.769
(Dramatic music)

03:05.105 --> 03:10.118
( ♪ )

